Reward:¶

  • Diamonds larger than 5 carats: half million dollars
  • Diamonds larger than 1 carat: 5000 dollars
  • Other small Diamonds: 100 dollars

Found Chances:¶

  • Diamonds larger than 5 carats: 7 out of a million
  • Diamonds larger than 1 carat: 0.0001
  • Other small Diamonds: 0.005

Expected Value¶

https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Expected_value

$$\Large E[X]=x_1p_1+\cdots+x_np_n$$

Expected Reward¶

$$\Large E[Reward] = 0.5\times7+5000\times0.0001+100\times0.005=4.5$$

Park admission fee is 15 dollars. Worth it???¶
